Add Model trait implementation to the filepicker component for file system navigation.

## Model Implementation

### init()
- Read initial directory contents
- Return Cmd to load directory listing asynchronously

### update(msg)
Handle these messages:
- `KeyMsg` - Navigation (up/down/enter/backspace)
- `DirectoryLoadedMsg(Vec<DirEntry>)` - Receive directory contents
- `SelectMsg` - Confirm file selection
- `FilterMsg(String)` - Filter visible files
- `ErrorMsg(io::Error)` - Handle filesystem errors

Return commands:
- Load directory command on navigation
- Selection complete command
- Error notification commands

### view()
- Render file/directory list with cursor
- Show current path
- Indicate selected item
- Show file permissions/size if configured

## Messages
```rust
pub enum FilePickerMsg {
    Key(KeyEvent),
    DirectoryLoaded(Vec<DirEntry>),
    Select,
    Filter(String),
    Error(io::Error),
}
```

